{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"洛阳有两大特色，不可不知。","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":31,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"首先就是以南北为中轴，让洛水横贯全城，把洛阳分为南北两区，以四座大桥接连，而城内洛水又与其他伊、涧三水联接城内，使城内河道萦绕，把山水之秀移至城内，予人天造地设的浑成感觉。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":35,"line_end":37},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我见惯江南的水乡城镇，多引江湖之水贯城而过，本没甚稀奇，但却少有如洛水般宽深笔直，使洛阳别具严整调谐的气象，而此城的规模，当然亦非水乡城市可比。另一特色又是甚么呢？","tone":"欣喜","chapter":140,"line_start":41,"line_end":43},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"另一特色就是在外郭城的西墙外，因其天然环境设置西苑，西至新安，北抵邙山，南达伊阙诸山，周围二百馀里，比得上古时汉武帝的上林苑，外郭城与西苑连在一起，令洛阳更具规模。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":49,"line_end":51},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"这座叫新中桥，只看此桥的规模，便具体而微地说明了杨广当年如何劳民伤财。据说为了使洛阳具都城之实，那昏君从全国各地迁来了数万户富商巨贾，又将河南三千多家工艺户安置到郭城东南隅的洛河南岸十二坊居住，所以眼前才有此气象。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":55,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"这叫坏心肠作好事，异日不论谁人得到天下，将会享受到杨广的建设成果，只要管治上稍为得法，盛世可期。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":61,"line_end":63},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"我们好应找个地方医医肚子了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":67,"line_end":67},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"我们必须作出些假像，才可令李密确信我们有出兵虎牢的决心。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":81,"line_end":83},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"我驻重兵于偃师，难道还不足够吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":140,"line_start":85,"line_end":85},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"那也可视作加强防守，且又不能予敌人放火烧粮的机会。我刚才研究过尚书给我的地理形势图，虎牢、荥阳皆位于洛水和大河之南，不若尚书着人在此城之东洛水两岸的适合河段设立浮桥，建立两、三座也不嫌多，然后在南岸设粮仓建军营，这种高姿态比任何军队调动更有显示力，亦免了李密要大动干戈攻城之苦。哈！此计如何？","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":87,"line_end":91},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"如此妙计，教我怎能拒绝呢？","tone":"无奈","chapter":140,"line_start":93,"line_end":95},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"锋寒兄似乎对洛阳份外欣赏，对吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":140,"line_start":99,"line_end":99}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ba_feng_han","name":"跋锋寒","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"跋锋寒，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及跋锋寒"}]},{"id":"char_wang_shi_chong","name":"王世充","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"王世充，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及王世充"}]},{"id":"char_dong_ming_gong_zhu_dan_wan_jing","name":"东溟公主单琬晶","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"东溟公主单琬晶，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及东溟公主单琬晶"}]},{"id":"char_qian_du_guan","name":"钱独关","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"钱独关，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及钱独关"}]},{"id":"char_li_yuan","name":"李渊","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"李渊，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及李渊"}]},{"id":"char_du_fu_wei","name":"杜伏威","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"杜伏威，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及杜伏威"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_xian","name":"萧铣","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"萧铣，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及萧铣"}]},{"id":"char_duan_yu_cheng","name":"段玉成","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"段玉成，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及段玉成"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"中土的城市里，我对洛阳和长安特别有印象，皆因两城均有王者之气，非一般城市可比拟。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":101,"line_end":103},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"江都又如何呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":140,"line_start":105,"line_end":105},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"我尚未到过江都，那是子陵你出身的地方，自然培养出深厚的感情，就像我对草原和大漠。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":107,"line_end":109},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"不过相比之下，我都是比较欢喜北方的城市和山水，那种险峻雄奇，和南方的绮丽明媚，是完全不同的味道，且较合我的脾胃。","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":111,"line_end":113},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"跋兄就像北方的大河峻岭，经得起风霜岁月的考验，不怕面对艰苦恶劣的环境。我和仲少毕竟是南方人，很易生出好逸恶劳之心，纵使练武，也没有甚么严格规律，嘻！","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":115,"line_end":119},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"我看寇仲比较近似我，而你亦非好逸恶劳，只是本性不喜与人争斗，但假若有人惹得你动了真火，我也要为那人担心！","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":121,"line_end":123},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我是那么可怕吗？","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":125,"line_end":125},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"我少有欣赏一个人，但你却是例外。平时你看来温文尔雅，好像事事都不放在心上，可是每到生死存亡的危急关头，你总能显出坚毅不拨之意志，并有却敌脱身之妙计，否则我们今早就不能在洛阳这里吃点心了。","tone":"严肃","chapter":140,"line_start":127,"line_end":131},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我倒没想过自己这方面的事，是了！我们是否应设法与仲少取得联络呢？","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":133,"line_end":135},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"仲少和王世充的交易如何，现今该已成定局，我们实不宜介入闻问。最好由寇仲来找我们。而我们只须照原先的约定留下标志，使他知道我们在那里就成了。","tone":"犹豫","chapter":140,"line_start":137,"line_end":141},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"那我们眼前干甚么好呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":143,"line_end":145},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"子陵你太不习惯没有寇仲的日子了，告诉我，以前你和寇仲一起时，有没有想过要干甚么或不干甚么的心境？","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":147,"line_end":149},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"真的似乎有点不习惯，不过凡事都有开始的，唉！待会！嘿！","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":151,"line_end":153},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"我们先去见一位我们都认识的美人儿，看看会否有你瑜姨的消息，顺便探听和氏璧的最新情况，子陵意下如何呢？","tone":"淡然","chapter":140,"line_start":157,"line_end":159},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我们都认识的美人儿？","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":161,"line_end":161},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"东溟公主单琬晶大概可算其中之一吧。","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":163,"line_end":165},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"甚么？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":140,"line_start":167,"line_end":167},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"尚书可知李密曾私访襄阳的钱独关，说动他供应人力粮草予他从南方攻打洛阳的部队吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":171,"line_end":173},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"钱独关难道不怕死？竟如此斗胆。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":175,"line_end":175},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"李密一向以智计闻名，他故意策动四大寇与江淮军合作，攻陷竟陵，胁迫北方诸城，实是一石二鸟之计，既可使杜伏威无暇兼顾南方，亦使洛阳以南数城因畏惧江淮军而投向他。所以尚书若不及早击破瓦岗军，早晚会给他团团围困，那就悔之已晚。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":177,"line_end":181},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"寇小兄为何能对南北形势如此清楚？","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":183,"line_end":183},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"当然是为了对付李密，这老贼颁下的'蒲山公令'，累得我两兄弟屡陷险境，几次险死还生，此獠岂能不灭。","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":185,"line_end":187},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"假若今仗胜不了李密，我是否应西联李渊？","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":189,"line_end":191},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"李渊、李密两者，尚书以为谁更可怕点呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":140,"line_start":193,"line_end":195}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ba_feng_han","name":"跋锋寒","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"跋锋寒，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及跋锋寒"}]},{"id":"char_wang_shi_chong","name":"王世充","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"王世充，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及王世充"}]},{"id":"char_dong_ming_gong_zhu_dan_wan_jing","name":"东溟公主单琬晶","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"东溟公主单琬晶，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及东溟公主单琬晶"}]},{"id":"char_qian_du_guan","name":"钱独关","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"钱独关，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及钱独关"}]},{"id":"char_li_yuan","name":"李渊","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"李渊，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及李渊"}]},{"id":"char_du_fu_wei","name":"杜伏威","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"杜伏威，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及杜伏威"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_xian","name":"萧铣","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"萧铣，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及萧铣"}]},{"id":"char_duan_yu_cheng","name":"段玉成","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"段玉成，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及段玉成"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":245,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"尚书已很清楚李阀的形势，也该知李世民乃胸怀平定中原大志的人。所以除非尚书肯俯首称臣，否则如让李世民在关中再多取得几处立足据点，洛阳早晚要落到他手上去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":205,"line_end":209},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"洛阳固是天下漕运交通的枢纽，但也因而陷于四面受敌的环境中，即使去掉李密，还要应付四方八面而来的攻击，非像李阀般进可攻退可守。","tone":"无奈","chapter":140,"line_start":211,"line_end":213},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"所以去李密之胁后，尚书必须用兵关中，至不济也要制得李阀半步都踏不出潼关，而尚书则可挟胜李密的馀威利用运河之便，逐步蚕食附近城镇，增加实力，舍此外再无他法。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":215,"line_end":217},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"我有点累了！想到舱内歇歇。","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":219,"line_end":219},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"天津晓月乃洛阳八景之首，最迷人是夜阑人静，明月挂空之时，携美来此把臂同游，个中滋味，当是一言难述。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":225,"line_end":227},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我忽然想起一事，恐怕难陪锋寒兄去见公主了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":229,"line_end":231},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"不知子陵兄有甚么急事呢？","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":233,"line_end":233},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"锋寒兄勿要以为我在找藉口避见公主，而是心挂失散了的兄弟，所以想去试试寻找他们。","tone":"微笑","chapter":140,"line_start":235,"line_end":237},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"你是指段玉成他们四人吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":239,"line_end":239},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"正是他们。","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":241,"line_end":241},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":null,"text":"如此便不阻子陵了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":140,"line_start":243,"line_end":243}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ba_feng_han","name":"跋锋寒","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"跋锋寒，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及跋锋寒"}]},{"id":"char_wang_shi_chong","name":"王世充","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"王世充，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及王世充"}]},{"id":"char_dong_ming_gong_zhu_dan_wan_jing","name":"东溟公主单琬晶","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"东溟公主单琬晶，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及东溟公主单琬晶"}]},{"id":"char_qian_du_guan","name":"钱独关","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"钱独关，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及钱独关"}]},{"id":"char_li_yuan","name":"李渊","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"李渊，身份未知","personality":{"traits":["未知"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":140,"line_start":1,"line_end":1,"text":"提及李渊"}]},{"id":"char_du_fu_wei","name":"杜伏威","alias":[],"identity":"未知","faction":"未知","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"杜伏威，身份未知","personality":{"trait